Actors List
1️⃣ Customer (Primary Actor)

Sends emails to the e-commerce support system

Receives automated responses

Interacts with:

Submit Customer Email

Receive Automated Reply

2️⃣ Support Executive

Handles emails that cannot be resolved automatically

Interacts with:

View Email Logs

Handle Forwarded Emails

3️⃣ System Administrator

Maintains the system configuration

Interacts with:

Manage Keywords

Manage Response Templates

View Logs
